== Glitches ==

=== Damage Boost Skip ===

A frame-perfect technique to skip through walls using enemy damage.

<pre>
Requirements:
- Low HP (any damage kills you is best timing)
- Enemy with knockback attack
- Wall you want to pass through

Execution:
1. Position hero 1 pixel from wall edge
2. Face perpendicular to wall
3. Get hit by enemy at exact frame
4. Hold direction through wall during i-frames
5. If done correctly, clip through
</pre>

