=== Soul Dupe ===

Rare glitch allowing souls to be released twice:

<pre>
Requirements:
- Lair with multiple monsters
- Kill last two monsters on same frame
- Soul release animation plays twice
- Soul counter increments twice
- Can reach 92+ souls (normally 91 max)
</pre>

=== Walk Through Walls ===

Using the scroll lock exploit:

<pre>
Location: Any scroll-locked area edge
Method:
1. Walk to screen edge during scroll lock
2. Pause game at exact frame screen tries to scroll
3. Unpause while holding opposite direction
4. Character position desyncs from collision
5. Walk through walls until next screen transition
</pre>

=== Magic Skip ===

Skip magic animations with menu:

<pre>
1. Cast any magic
2. Open menu during cast animation
3. Close menu immediately
4. Magic effect applies without full animation
5. Saves ~2 seconds per cast
</pre>

